#- From Aged Cognac to Zinfandel, there is a wine for everyone.§0
§0
§0Grapes have the widest variety of, brews made from a single ingredient.§0
§0
§0The first edition covers 9 wines and spirits. Research may continue; I'd love a nice Chianti.
#- §l     Brewing Tips§0
§0
§0Measure out your ingredients in advance.§0
§0
§0Right-click with a gold clock for exact timing.§0
§0
§0If it doesn't need a barrel, don't use one!§0
§0
§0Wines may overlap; precision is key.
