#- The recipes here were all tested with grapes harvested from the vineyards of CivCorp and Wheatistan.§0
§0
§0Grapes can be cut from most vines east of Tel Adam.§0
§0
§0The vineyard must be built on solid land, with only sky above, or you'll only get vines.
#- §oI don't always drink wine, but when I do, I refer to the book:§0
